                translation: "H?m nay t?i ?i si?u th?. T?i mua b?nh m?. T?i mua s?a. T?i v? nh?. T?i ?n b?nh m?. T?i u?ng s?a.",
                highlightedWords: [
                    {word: 'スーパー', meaning: 'si?u th?'},
                    {word: 'パン', meaning: 'b?nh m?'},
